{"tid":1378574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7.28 賽後檢討！","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:24:36.000Z","uid":211102,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e1fdf6224062f42aeeb479948c2e8212936be7df","tid":1378574,"uid":211102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:10:44.000Z","msg":"又係時候賽後檢討<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發夢係林市街停車場 發現有幾樣野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 上中前線要用豬嘴</span></span><br />\n用左豬嘴 能力加乘好多<br />\n唔洗一放催淚彈就散<br />\n有啲人真係得外科口罩<br />\n一中就好大獲<br />\n同埋而家啲蛋亂鳩咁射 後排都會中<br />\n所以買定保護自己 減少大家負擔<br />\n個心都定啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 人同人留返啲空位</span></span><br />\n太多人停係內街<br />\n搞到前面要退果時真心退唔到<br />\n啲人密到抖唔到氣咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 留意旗手</span></span><br />\n今次第一次用旗手<br />\n我自己覺得幾好 又有共識<br />\n但一亂有人係有留意旗手 直跑咁濟<br />\n所以記住睇一睇旗手示出黎既狀態<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 濕毛巾同鹽水每人都帶定先</span></span><br />\n一來沖眼 二來滅催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但警察開槍堅係冇計<br />\n而家好比人瘋狂掃射咁<br />\n要諗諗佢</span>"},{"pid":"fcbb2b5807ed3e3b238eb65173ff1603ab203508","tid":1378574,"uid":75056,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:12:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">人同人留返啲空位</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a7fce6a2e73738e1faa209cb806584c3ca216576","tid":1378574,"uid":211102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dae394ada436b6b1da2dd10a98ede9d824dde404","tid":1378574,"uid":96945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:12:54.000Z","msg":"認清事實，咪再下下想靠國際，靠自己！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/drNxeS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/drNxeS</a>"},{"pid":"61e7200849a206dd12db50752519ed70207688f0","tid":1378574,"uid":292722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:13:08.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">〈光復香港 時代革命〉\n\n我冇野講 我有權唔解鎖\n我要搵律師 (背定律師電話)\n我唔簽任何文件 我要警誡記錄\n我要食飯 飲水 毛氈 去廁所\n我唔舒服要去醫院\n我要睇你委任證同編號</code></pre>"},{"pid":"32a359a94e98750ff0c943d3996cdbf596b15366","tid":1378574,"uid":145593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:13:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b27fda44b83b81b093982146e5975e928c67657","tid":1378574,"uid":138116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b6829b5c0c4133c763a0f862f6e816bfab8fa1","tid":1378574,"uid":31111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:15:51.000Z","msg":"人同人之間真係要留空位，睇直播最前個班比速龍突襲，後面太多人搞到最前比狗打，後面又跌倒，差啲人踩人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac62a565918b162c1fae51f930c4b2b74fb9ad7","tid":1378574,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:15:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280576497855cb17dcb7a68b7da4d143cb540c7f","tid":1378574,"uid":225649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:16:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377649/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377649/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12fc5a02b8b9468170a66e09fe799aa6b053b31","tid":1378574,"uid":211102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8b27fda44b83b81b093982146e5975e928c67657","tid":1378574,"uid":138116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:16:43.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f92ebaa6dc0d5ccc5d93273fc7960b5416be2f","tid":1378574,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:17:24.000Z","msg":"唔好再分開行動,齊上齊落,要懂得睇形勢勿暖戰"},{"pid":"8f12d9a3b926850cc8699283917a0a6e3474a523","tid":1378574,"uid":47905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"其實最大問題係分左兩個地方<br />\n<br />\n一邊唔肯去增援<br />\n另一邊唔肯退<br />\n<br />\n黑警集中打殘一邊<br />\n另一邊都廢事理<br />\n<br />\n呢D情況應該需要有共識<br />\n到底過去定係退<br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得應該退<br />\n退返去無警個邊守<br />\n<br />\n因為無警個邊有更多時間整到條防線"},{"pid":"f9d14904fb5fab8ce86fdc077aa995ba47008c3d","tid":1378574,"uid":16374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:18:55.000Z","msg":"Agger豬嘴<br />\n<br />\n最近先入手 90蚊個<br />\n用左好好多 有機會聞到少少 <br />\n但起碼唔會太刺激頂唔順<br />\n<br />\n以下post有reference教點買<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>［和理非入] 買一套100%防禦既豬嘴目鏡都係百幾蚊!!! 保護自已=保護他人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359346</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8d9f9548c4f6d2fb89e67a6e65d1acfc62df0ad8","tid":1378574,"uid":211102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fac62a565918b162c1fae51f930c4b2b74fb9ad7","tid":1378574,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:15:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7715cf018a8959efb6060101de70bc6c347b95dc","tid":1378574,"uid":235711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:19:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6e9cb551594abe07f096322e54c6ae517e203f0","tid":1378574,"uid":277441,"like":0,"dislik